{"tid":2159842,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"《幻愛》現實版—情侶同患解離症 11個人格的相愛與對峙「我哋連點認識都唔知」","createTime":"2020-08-16T14:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T12:47:35.000Z","uid":113250,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"48b185a147bbb68a914be447acb6aa0c9468435c","tid":2159842,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T14:39:22.000Z","msg":"《幻愛》現實版&mdash;情侶同患解離症 11個人格的相愛與對峙「我哋連點認識都唔知」<span class=\"x-small\"> (果籽 Appledaily)</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4Jc93fJLdQI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4Jc93fJLdQI&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJIL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=b07f8912\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4Jc93fJLdQI</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">「我們的相識是個謎。」同患人格解離症的他們如此形容自己的愛情。何時何地認識、彼此說的第一句話、哪裏得知對方地址，他們統統不知情。忽然一天，二人收到對方的信件，你叫陳寶珊，我叫方浩天，「天珊一對」，彷彿是天作之合。兩人成為既陌生又親密的筆友，聊起生活瑣事、談談喜怒哀樂、細訴混沌情緒&hellip;&hellip;六年來陪對方經歷驚濤駭浪，每次講起奇情的相遇，二人都說莫名其妙。<br />\n<br />\n二十四歲的寶珊和二十七歲的浩天同樣患上解離性身份疾患（Dissociative Identity Disorder），各自也有幾個不同年紀、性格、喜好的人格，一個身體彷彿住了幾個靈魂。當不同人格走出來時，主人格會斷片，遺失了某段記憶和時間，忘記自己去過哪裏做過甚麼，瞬間已過了幾小時甚至幾天，醒來時發現，不是衣櫃多了件不屬於自己的衣服，就是被朋友投訴爽約，「解離症最痛苦是沒法控制其他人格走不走出來，或下一秒出來的是誰、會做些甚麼，像一個母親要照顧幾個女兒。」寶珊說。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇完眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67d7683efe0cc917de58f4dc3f79709012534f8e","tid":2159842,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T14:39:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f57d7d56dc297e791eee162a0e167620023c4e05","tid":2159842,"uid":64601,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T14:41:34.000Z","msg":"陳寶珊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原來有真人相"},{"pid":"01b9398490eb494c847ba3826152ee80f3e0ad03","tid":2159842,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f57d7d56dc297e791eee162a0e167620023c4e05","tid":2159842,"uid":64601,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T14:41:34.000Z","msg":"陳寶珊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原來有真人相"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T14:45:13.000Z","msg":"咁多人格唔怪得個個都...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20a70733ef1d8879f93d83fb8b7479587087a28","tid":2159842,"uid":134103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T14:56:42.000Z","msg":"天珊一對<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好浪漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a547994f2f9e78e29829597533b5b8612aee880","tid":2159842,"uid":263949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T14:58:00.000Z","msg":"好難完全明白佢哋嘅生活<br />\n好似每日一起身就會唔同咗好多 <br />\n因為永遠都唔知另外啲人格做咗啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd0e0d87c3b96e609f18fd90a6c105e8634b7d25","tid":2159842,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T15:50:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9171067c0a7d96193be40dbf87981af3dcc6cc4","tid":2159842,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T12:45:02.000Z","msg":"真係超癲 ...  <br />\n一個人幾個人格 <br />\n<br />\n仲要一個人格出現 ,   個主人會